biography_text: PHILLIPS, Dean, a Representative from Minnesota; born in St. Paul, Ramsey County, Minn., January 20, 1969; graduated from The Blake School, Hopkins, Minn., 1987; B.A., Brown University, Providence, R.I., 1991; M.B.A., University of Minnesota, Minneapolis, Minn., 2000; businessman; elected as a Democrat to the One Hundred Sixteenth Congress (January 3, 2019-present).
